---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Home
---

<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="min-h-[85vh] sm:min-h-[90vh] flex items-center">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 sm:py-24">
    <p class="label mb-4 sm:mb-6">Early Stage · Multi-Sector</p>
    
    <h1 class="headline-caps text-3xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl mb-6 sm:mb-8 max-w-4xl">
      Venture capital for<br>
      creators and builders at<br>
      the technology frontier
    </h1>
    
    <p class="text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl text-white/50 max-w-xl mb-8 sm:mb-12 leading-relaxed">
      We back technical founders at the earliest stages, partnering on infrastructure the world will rely on for decades.
    </p>
    
    <!-- Sector list -->
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-3 sm:gap-x-4 gap-y-2">
      {% for sector in site.sectors %}
      <span class="text-xs sm:text-sm font-mono" style="color: {{ sector.color }}">{{ sector.name | lower }}</span>
      {% if not loop.last %}<span class="text-white/20">·</span>{% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Portfolio Preview -->
<section class="py-16 sm:py-24 border-t border-white/10">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-8 sm:mb-12">
      <p class="label">Portfolio</p>
      <a href="/portfolio/" class="text-sm text-white/60 hover:text-white transition-colors">View all →</a>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-3 sm:gap-4">
      {% for company in portfolio %}
      <a href="{{ company.url or '#' }}" 
         class="group p-4 sm:p-6 rounded-lg border border-white/10 hover:border-white/20 bg-lv-bg-secondary transition-all"
         {% if company.url %}target="_blank" rel="noopener"{% endif %}>
        <span class="sector-tag" style="color: {{ company.color }}">{{ company.code }}</span>
        <h3 class="company-name text-xl sm:text-2xl mt-2 sm:mt-3 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">{{ company.name }}</h3>
        <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-white/40 mt-2 line-clamp-2">{{ company.description }}</p>
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Thesis Preview -->
<section class="py-16 sm:py-24 border-t border-white/10">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 sm:gap-16">
      <div>
        <p class="label mb-4 sm:mb-6">Our Approach</p>
        <h2 class="headline-caps text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-4 sm:mb-6">
          Systematic capital<br>deployment
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed mb-4 sm:mb-6 text-sm sm:text-base">
          We invest in technical founders building foundational infrastructure across AI, crypto, defense, education, energy, and health. Our focus is on the earliest stages—pre-seed through Series A—where conviction matters more than consensus.
        </p>
        <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed mb-6 sm:mb-8 text-sm sm:text-base">
          We look for founders with deep technical expertise, clear insight into an underserved market, and the tenacity to build something that will outlast market cycles.
        </p>
        <a href="/thesis/" class="text-sm text-white/60 hover:text-white transition-colors">Read our thesis →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
